transformations.description: This source is a Insured query using. The first portion of the query will use the note_stg, plicy_risk_key_reference , application_stg  and join with target uw_dashboard_flag_note_details to get SC2
transformations.name: src_query

object.customQuery:
select
	distinct 
	prkr.policy_system_id,
	prkr.policy_number,
	prkr.policy_module_number,
	prkr.policy_key,
	n.system_id as note_system_id,
	n.cmm_container as note_cmm_container,
	n.parent_id as note_parent_id,
	n.id as note_id,
	n.status as note_status,
	n.sticky_ind as note_sticky_indicator,
	n.description as note_description,
	n.memo as note_memo,
        n.template_id as note_template_id,
        n.add_dt as note_add_date,
        n.add_user as note_add_user, 
        n.category as note_category,
	nd.uw_dashboard_flag_note_details_row_id,
	nd.uw_dashboard_flag_note_details_md5_hash_value
from
	(
	select
		system_id,
		cmm_container,
		id,
		parent_id,
		row_id,
		sticky_ind,
		status,
		description,
		memo,
                template_id,
                add_dt,
                add_user, 
                category,
		rank() over (partition by system_id,
		id
	order by
		sticky_ind,
		row_id desc) as rnk
	from
		dbo.note_stg) n
left join dbo.policy_risk_key_reference prkr
on
	n.system_id = prkr.policy_system_id
	and n.cmm_container = prkr.policy_cmm_container
left join dbo.uw_dashboard_flag_note_details nd	
on
	n.system_id = nd.note_system_id
	and n.cmm_container = nd.note_cmm_container
	and n.parent_id = nd.note_parent_id
	and n.id = nd.note_id
	and nd.uw_dashboard_flag_note_details_row_effective_end_datetime = '9999-12-31'
where
	  prkr.policy_risk_key_reference_row_effective_end_date = '9999-12-31'
	and n.cmm_container = 'Application'
	and n.rnk = 1
union
select
	distinct 
	prkr.policy_system_id,
	prkr.policy_number,
	prkr.policy_module_number,
	prkr.policy_key,
	n.system_id as note_system_id,
	n.cmm_container as note_cmm_container,
	n.parent_id as note_parent_id,
	n.id as note_id,
	n.status as note_status,
	n.sticky_ind as note_sticky_indicator,
	n.description as note_description,
	n.memo as note_memo,
        n.template_id as note_template_id,
        n.add_dt as note_add_date,
        n.add_user as note_add_user, 
        n.category as note_category,
	nd.uw_dashboard_flag_note_details_row_id,
	nd.uw_dashboard_flag_note_details_md5_hash_value
from
	(
	select
		system_id,
		cmm_container,
		id,
		parent_id,
		row_id,
		sticky_ind,
		status,
		description,
		memo,
                template_id,
                add_dt,
                add_user, 
                category,
		rank() over (partition by system_id,
		id
	order by
		sticky_ind,
		row_id desc) as rnk
	from
		dbo.note_stg) n
left join dbo.policy_risk_key_reference prkr
on
	n.system_id = prkr.policy_system_id
	and n.cmm_container = prkr.policy_cmm_container
left join dbo.uw_dashboard_flag_note_details nd
on
	n.system_id = nd.note_system_id
	and n.cmm_container = nd.note_cmm_container
	and n.parent_id = nd.note_parent_id
	and n.id = nd.note_id
	and nd.uw_dashboard_flag_note_details_row_effective_end_datetime = '9999-12-31'
where
	prkr.policy_risk_key_reference_row_effective_end_date = '9999-12-31'
	and n.cmm_container = 'Policy'
	and n.rnk = 1

fields.expression:
MD5('policy_system_id'|| policy_system_id ||
	'policy_number' || policy_number ||
    'policy_module_number' || policy_module_number ||
	'policy_key' || policy_key ||
	'note_system_id' || note_system_id ||
	'note_cmm_container' || note_cmm_container ||
	'note_parent_id' || note_parent_id ||
	'note_id' || note_id ||
	'note_status' || note_status ||
	'note_sticky_indicator' || note_sticky_indicator ||
	'note_description' || note_description ||
    'note_memo' || note_memo || 
    'note_template_id' || note_template_id || 
    'note_add_date' || note_add_date || 
    'note_add_user' || note_add_user || 
    'note_category' || note_category)
